# =============================================================================
# Zola SSG — .gitignore
# GitHub Actions (.github/) is intentionally NOT ignored — required for CI/CD.
# =============================================================================

# --- Zola build output ---
# Regenerated by `zola build` on every CI push (peaceiris/actions-gh-pages).
# Never commit this directory.
public/

# --- Reference documents (local only) ---
# PDFs, research books, local notes not needed for the build.
book/

# --- macOS system artifacts ---
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# --- Linux / editor temp files ---
*~
*.swp
*.swo
.*.sw?

# --- VS Code ---
.vscode/

# --- JetBrains IDEs ---
.idea/

# --- Node / npx cache ---
# npx is used for one-off tooling (svgo, etc.) — cache is local only.
node_modules/
.npm/
package-lock.json

# --- Zola themes (if using Git submodules, .gitmodules is tracked, not content) ---
# themes/* would be managed as submodules if needed.
# Currently empty — nothing to ignore here.
